data.description: Attention Investors!!! Investment opportunity. This charming two-story home welcomes you with a large front porch including a ramp. As you enter, the living room offers tall ceilings and a decorative fireplace mantle while the dining room has beautiful built-in wood shelving and cabinets. Along with the living and dining rooms, the kitchen, bathroom, and laundry area are all on the first floor. You will be pleasantlysurprised by two large bedrooms with plenty of closet space on the second floor. This home includes a covered back patio with a Summer Kitchen-type shed and a detached one car garage. Welcome Home!
